te> Fri, 19 May 2023 14:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/price-of-life-hryvnia-styled-leaflets-rain-on-kiev-militants-1110462699.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/price-of-life-hryvnia-styled-leaflets-rain-on-kiev-militants-1110462699.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>心理战</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[China-Central Asia Summit: Beijing Becoming 'More Consequential Player on Global Stage']]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110462550" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110461383_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_42ee9e373c7e90f0732a19650f40ddb0.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1110461365" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/china-central-asia-summit-beijing-becoming-more-consequential-player-on-global-stage-1110462550.html?share-img=1110461365"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / FLORENCE LO</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">中国国家主席习近平于 2023 年 5 月 19 日在中国陕西省西安市举行的中国-中亚峰会期间合影留念</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="Chinese President Xi Jinping waves during a group photo session during the China-Central Asia Summit in Xian, in China's northern Shaanxi province on May 19, 2023 - Sputnik International, 1920, 19.05.2023" title="2023 年 5 月 19 日，中国国家主席习近平在中国陕西省西安市举行的中国-中亚峰会期间合影留念" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110461383_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_0103bb64d20d3ebd94a799fc3984f17b.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110461383_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_102e801ee2130e532cab3f6a9b15cb2e.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110461383_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_9443fe121781cbc5c15ade346dac3e1d.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/13/1110461383_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_0103bb64d20d3ebd94a799fc3984f17b.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©<a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">法新社 2023</a> / FLORENCE LO </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Oleg Burunov - Sputnik International" title="奥列格布鲁诺夫" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/09/0b/1080424846_0:0:2048:2048_100x100_80_0_0_3d7b461f8a98586fa3fe739930816aea.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">奥列格布鲁诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_burunov_oleg/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:o.burunov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">卡塔尔乔治敦大学政府学教授梅赫兰·卡姆拉瓦 (Mehran Kamrava) 告诉卫星通讯社，就北京扩大其国际影响力而言，中国主办西安峰会“至关重要”。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周五举行了两次高级别区域会议：在西安举行的中国-中亚峰会和在沙特阿拉伯吉达<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230514/syrian-delegates-arrive-in-jeddah-ahead-of-arab-league-summit---source-1110351619.html" target="_blank">举行的阿拉伯联盟峰会</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这些事件发生之际，加拿大、法国、德国、日本、意大利、英国和美国的领导人齐聚广岛参加 G7 峰会。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">卡姆拉瓦说，尽管七国集团仍然是一个能让其成员坐下来讨论协调政策的机构，但这“不再意味着他们可以决定全球经济的健康或福祉或方向”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “这不再意味着他们可以决定全球秩序的形态，或者他们可以在全球层面制定具有重大影响的政策，”教授争辩道，并补充说 G7 现在不能被视为“全球决定性力量，因为它可能会喜欢。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110462550" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/china-central-asia-summit-beijing-becoming-more-consequential-player-on-global-stage-1110462550.html?share-block=1110462840" data-title="&amp;quot;It no longer means that they can decide the shape of the global order, or that they can have tremendously consequential policies at the global level,&amp;quot; the professor argued, adding that the G7 now cannot be considered &amp;quot;a globally-determining force as it might have liked to have been.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当被问及中国-中亚峰会的意义时，卡姆拉瓦称这次活动“相当重要”，这反映出北京“迟早发现了中亚共和国的战略意义”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位专家强调说：“我认为中国主办这次峰会至关重要，因为这再次表明 PCR 现在正在成为全球舞台上更重要的外交角色。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他补充说，中国是国际知名的“技术生产大国”、非洲重要的“商业参与者”和波斯湾的“重要参与者”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “现在我们看到的是中国确保它也是中亚重要的重要参与者。北京与中亚之间的地理、历史和后勤联系比中亚共和国与欧洲国家或其他国家之间的联系更加牢固。北美。中国正在利用这些后勤、交通、历史和文化联系来深化其在世界各地的外交活动，”卡姆拉瓦指出。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110462550" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/china-central-asia-summit-beijing-becoming-more-consequential-player-on-global-stage-1110462550.html?share-block=1110462841" data-title="&amp;quot;And now what we&amp;#x27;re seeing is China ensuring that it is also a consequential and significant player in Central Asia. The geographic, historical and logistical links between Beijing and Central Asia are much more robust than between Central Asian republics and countries in Europe or North America. And China is capitalizing on those logistical, transportation, historical and cultural links to deepen its diplomatic activity around the world,&amp;quot; Kamrava pointed out."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">莫斯科政治学家兼 HSE 大学教授德米特里·埃夫斯塔菲耶夫 (Dmitry Evstafiev) 在一定程度上赞同他的观点，他告诉卫星通讯社， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230509/new-era-of-cooperation-xi-jinping-to-chair-china-central-asia-summit-1110218163.html" target="_blank">中国-中亚峰会</a>作为讨论北京进军国际市场等问题的场所“非常重要”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/g7-hiroshima-summit-fading-bloc-sticking-to-its-guns-to-contain-china-russia-1110444787.html" target="_blank">G7 峰会</a>上，Evstafiev 称其具有“非创造性的格式，这是从过去继承下来的，目前被惯性所使用”。这位政治分析家强调 G7 模式“完全无条件地依赖美国”这一点。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “这种形式取决于美国的全球地缘政治能力，目前我认为这不是无条件有效和稳固的。所以问题是美国在目前的情况下是否能够提出一些新计划或新愿景G7。在我看来，它不会。这意味着这种 [G7] 形式将继续退回到历史的迷雾中，”这位政治学家总结道。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 14:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/china-central-asia-summit-beijing-becoming-more-consequential-player-on-global-stage-1110462550.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230519/china-central-asia-summit-beijing-becoming-more-consequential-player-on-global-stage-1110462550.html<category>亚洲</category><category>中国</category><category>沙特阿拉伯</category><category>日本</category><category>G7峰会</category><category>中亚</category><category>玩家</category><category>市场</category></item></channel></rss>